        <sect2 xml:id="new-provisional">
            <title>New Provisional Tools</title>
            <para>Sakai 2.2.0 has added four new provisional tools</para>
            <variablelist>
                <varlistentry>
                    <term>Message Center
                    </term>
                    <listitem><para>a tool combining a discussion forum with private messaging.</para></listitem>
                </varlistentry>
                <varlistentry>
                    <term>Search
                    </term>
                    <listitem><para>a tool providing a Google-like search of all site content.</para></listitem>
                </varlistentry>
                <varlistentry>
                    <term>Summary Calendar
                    </term>
                    <listitem><para>a synoptic calendar view for the MyWorkspace that includes events from all the sites to which a user is a member.</para></listitem>
                </varlistentry>
                <varlistentry>
                    <term>Post 'Em
                    </term>
